---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="site-footer">
  <div class="footer-inner">
    <p>
      This is an unofficial, non-commercial fan site. Warhammer 40,000,
      the Aquila logo, and all related names, characters, and artwork are
      trademarks and/or copyrights of Games Workshop Limited. All original
      summaries, notes, and opinions on this site are the author's own.
    </p>
    <p class="meta">&copy; {year} &mdash; Lore Archive (personal project)</p>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .site-footer {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .footer-inner {
    max-width: var(--max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  .footer-inner p {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .meta {
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
  }
</style>
